---
title: Tex-Mex Double Beef and Rice Skillet with Cheddar Cheese and Lime Crema
description: This colourful, no-fuss Tex-Mex skillet is packed with flavour, thanks to spiced rice and salsa-coated beef and peppers. Melty cheese and a dollop of sour cream are all you need to make your tastebuds sing!

